brutally killed by a mob.This after he stabbed his neighbour, accusing her of
practicing witchcraft.Police spokesperson Colonel Moetshe Ngoepe
said Josia Mukwevho (62) allegedly went to his neighbour and stabbed her with a
sharp instrument accusing her of practicing Witchcraft and fled the scene

